                        <item xml:id="e1">- Many omitted letters or words are inserted interlineally, in the main hand: e.g., fols. 11rb, 17rb, 24ra-b, 31ra, 39vb, 41ra, 48rb, 60ra, 75ra-b, 79vb.&#xD;
